### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8091/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get All Events (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

### Get All Events with Pagination (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?page=1&limit=10

### Get Event by ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1

### Create New Event (Auth Required - Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Rock Concert 2025",
  "description": "Amazing rock concert featuring top bands",
  "location": "Jakarta Convention Center",
  "date": "2025-12-31T20:00:00Z",
  "capacity": 5000,
  "price": 500000,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/concert.jpg"
}

### Update Event (Auth Required - Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Rock Concert 2025 - Updated",
  "description": "Amazing rock concert featuring top bands - UPDATED",
  "location": "Jakarta Convention Center - Hall A",
  "date": "2025-12-31T20:00:00Z",
  "capacity": 6000,
  "price": 550000,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/concert-updated.jpg"
}

### Delete Event (Auth Required - Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

